        &mo_tog KP KP     &kp GRAVE &kp CAPS &kp LEFT &kp RIGHT                &kp SPACE &none   &kp END              &kp PG_DN &kp DEL &kp BACKSPACE              &kp C_PLAY_PAUSE     &kp C_PREV     &kp C_NEXT    &kp RBKT        &mo FN
